You can hover over the trend lines for Created and Resolved to pop up the underlying data value.

The proposal is that you should also be able to hover over the "Trend of Unresolved" (if enabled) to pop up the underlying data value.  (I.e., do not make the user calculate the delta from the Created & Resolved data values at that time point).

-Johnny

